T1  - A Model of Product Design and Information Disclosure Investments
AU  - Markopoulos, Panos M.
AU  - Hosanagar, Kartik
Y1  - 2017/02/08
PY  - 2017
DA  - 2018/02/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2016.2634
